        <h3>
          <a href="/history/from-the-governors-mansion-to-the-white-house-and-beyond-rosalynn-carter-was-a-tireless-advocate-for-the-vulnerable-180982895/">
            From the Governor&#x27;s Mansion to the White House and Beyond, Rosalynn Carter Was a Tireless Advocate for the Vulnerable
          </a>
        </h3>

        
          
            <p class="article-dek">Smithsonian experts reflect on the life and legacy of the former first lady, who died Sunday at age 96</p>
          
          <p class="author">

  
    
      
        
        
          <a href='/author/meilan-solly/'>Meilan Solly</a>
        
      
      
    
  
</p>
        
