        <div class="special-item first-item">
          <a href="/smithsonian-institution/race-america-180978468/">
            <img loading="lazy" src="https://th-thumbnailer.cdn-si-edu.com/d80g8xPBYLZtPs_0Jd7UG1fUc90=/400x300/filters:no_upscale():focal(2485x1255:2486x1256)/https://tf-cmsv2-smithsonianmag-media.s3.amazonaws.com/filer_public/f2/37/f2373224-fab4-4ec7-a99e-e3d6cbcdfcc6/gettyimages-1280903151.jpg" alt="The Smithsonian&amp;#39;s Race and Our Shared Future: Reckoning With Our Racial Past initiative centers on six pillars." width="640" height="480" />
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="special-item second-item">
          <h2><a href="/smithsonian-institution/race-america-180978468/">Race in America</a></h2>
          <p>To mark the Smithsonian&#39;s multi-year initiative, <a href="https://oursharedfuture.si.edu/" target="_blank">Our Shared Future: Reckoning With Our Racial Past</a>, which will confront the history and legacy of race and racism through live and virtual events, pop-up exhibitions, digital resources, and other offerings, <em>Smithsonian</em> magazine has compiled this collection of relevant coverage.</p>
          <p class="section larger">
            <a href="/smithsonian-institution/race-america-180978468/">View Full Report <img src="/static/smithsonianmag/img/ArrowIcon.f9923e5f50ba.svg"></a>
          </p>
        </div>
